Installation in Archlinux：
    pacman -S opencv gtkglext hdf5 python-numpy
optional packages: opencl-icd-loader opencv-samples
explanation:
    hdf5是一种数据格式、可以存储不同类型的图像和数码数据
    NumPy是高性能科学计算和数据分析的基础包
    HighGUI是一个可以移植的图形工具包，显示图像，读写图像相关的文件
Configure opencv in eclipse:
    add include and add lib
    compiler path: /usr/include
    linker path: /usr/lib /usr/lib64, and add libraries' names: opencv_core opencv_imgproc opencv_imgcodecs opencv_highgui opencv_ml opencv_videoio opencv_video opencv_features2d opencv_calib3d opencv_objdetect opencv_flann

    灰度图=单通道图，彩色图=三通道图
    处理图片，除了对图片局部空间的分析，还有通道、图层等的信息（SCA-CNN）
    CVPR:https://www.jianshu.com/p/580564d654f5?utm_campaign=maleskine&utm_content=note&utm_medium=seo_notes&utm_source=recommendation

    


